<note n="0856009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856009"><g ref="#CB00096">𤬪</g><g ref="#CB01285">㼜</g>坊膩嘶＝<g ref="#CB00096">𤬪</g><unclear></unclear>垢膩<g ref="#CB00542">㽄</g>【三】，瓦甖垢膩斧【宮】</note>
<note n="0856010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856010">破＝斫【宮】</note>
<note n="0856011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856011">狖＝猫【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856012">兀＝<g ref="#CB09630">󲖞</g>【宋】，杌【元】【明】，瓦【宮】</note>
<note n="0856013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856013">污穢＝穢污【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856014">疽＝蛆【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856015">梟鵄＝鵄梟【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856016" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856016"><g ref="#CB02985">󰮩</g>＝<g ref="#CB02406">𣚦</g>【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856017" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856017">歧＝岐【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0856018" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856018">俠＝挾【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856019" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856019">趣＝道【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856020" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856020">火大＝大火【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856021" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856021">莫＝膜【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856022" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856022">到＝倒【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856023" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856023"><g ref="#CB02993">䫃</g>＝頑【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856024" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856024">愛＝受【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0856025" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856025"><g ref="#CB01485">㾽</g>＝贅【元】【明】，癰【宮】</note>
<note n="0856026" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856026">十八＝依止【宮】</note>
<note n="0856027" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0856027">〔欲〕－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857001">以＝已【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857002">焚＝炎【明】</note>
<note n="0857003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857003">宣＝揎【宋】【元】，捋【明】</note>
<note n="0857004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857004">毘紐＝毘沙紐【宋】【明】【宮】，毘沙細【元】</note>
<note n="0857005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857005">制控＝控制【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857006">耗＝<g ref="#CB00238">㧌</g>【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857007">發起＝起發【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857008">欻＝熾【三】</note>
<note n="0857009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857009">摩＝魔【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857010">葉＝業【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857011">空中＝室中【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0857012" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857012">迴覆＝洄覆【三】＊，洄<g ref="#CB13523">󳓓</g>【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0857013" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857013">糧米＝粳米【宮】</note>
<note n="0857014" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857014">此＝是【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0857015" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0857015">拔＝跋【三】【宮】</note>
